#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract message strings from UI and GUI-RC files"
msgstr "UI तथा GUI-RC सञ्चिकाभ्यः सन्देशस्ट्रिंग् निष्कासयन्तु"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> <group><option><replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command><group><option><replaceable> सञ्चिकानाम</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> finds all text tags and other message strings "
"in the given files and writes the corresponding i18n() calls to standard "
"output so that xgettext can parse them."
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command> दत्तसञ्चिकासु सर्वाणि पाठटैग्स् अन्यसन्देशताराः च अन्विष्य "
"तत्सम्बद्धानि i18n() आह्वानं मानकनिर्गमं प्रति लिखति येन xgettext तान् विश्लेषणं कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It understands both (&Qt;/&kde;) <application>designer</application>'s "
"<acronym>UI</acronym> files and &XML; GUI-RC files."
msgstr ""
"एतत् (&Qt;/&kde;) <application>designer</application> इत्यस्य <acronym>UI</"
"acronym> सञ्चिकाः &XML; GUI-RC सञ्चिकाः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr "इयं उपयोगिता KDE Software Development Kit इत्यस्य भागः अस्ति ।"
